code: import axios from'axios';import{YDATALOADING,YDATALOADED,YDATASEARCH}from'./types';export var loadYData=function loadYData(){return function(dispatch,getState){dispatch({type:YDATALOADING});axios.get('http://localhost:8000/youtube/api').then(function(res){dispatch({type:YDATALOADED,payload:res.data});}).catch(function(err){console.log(err);});};};export var searchData=function searchData(query){return function(dispatch,getState){dispatch({type:YDATASEARCH});axios.get("http://localhost:8000/youtube/api/find?search=".concat(query)).then(function(res){dispatch({type:YDATASEARCH,payload:res.data});}).catch(function(err){console.log(err);});};};
